<br>
Certainly the zekkers are planning to do twink moves and powerlevelling. I haven't ready any FV'ers planning for it. <br>
<br>
Oh, and if you didn't think it was bad enough, to add insult to injury, you can also create a character on Stormhammer and if you cancel have it moved to any server you'd like.<br>
<br>
In all honesty, I don't think Sony knows what the hell they are doing with all of this. This whole thing smells like a Dilbert idea that got tossed out at some meeting and that a pointy haired boss gave the unconditional green flag to.<br>
<br>
Currently there's apparently no way to edit or change character moves. <br>
<br>
The date has already been pushed back once. <br>
<br>
There are bugs in the movepages not allowing people to move all the characters they want. Other people aren't running into these difficulties.<br>
<br>
Confirmation emails are not going out for final moves. The confirmation emails that are going out to arrange moves come from an address that doesn't really exist and that bounces mail if replied to.<br>
<br>
Take a look at how you switch back to regular EQ: you cancel your entire EQ account, then when your current term runs out, your account is cancelled and your characters are moved back to their original blue servers or wherever you'd like the ones you created on Stormhammer to go. Huh?! &quot;Hello?!&quot; What if your account gets cancelled due to a billing error or your card number changed or something? Will you be locked out of Legends forever? If you are trying to cancel and have a new toon on Stormhammer, how will VI know where you want that toon to go when you are not a subscriber to EQ?! Will VI really make a priority of moving characters back for people who don't even subscribe to the game? This is a complete crackpot idea.<br>
<br>
I don't honestly know who's running the Legends show, but I don't think it's well thought out. <br>
<br>
This is going to be a debacle. <p><table border=0 cellpadding=4 cellspacing=0><tr><td><img src="http://home.tampabay.rr.com/legolaas/images/numtini-100.jpg" width="52" height="100"></td><td><table style="font-family:verdana,arial;" border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0><tr><td style="font-size:10pt;"><A HREF="http://pub94.ezboard.com/unumtini.showPublicProfile?language=EN" title="<insert popup caption here>" style="color:#ff0000;font-weight:700;">Numtini Lightheart</A></td></tr><tr><td style="font-size:10pt;">46th Season Gnome of Death</td></tr><tr><td style="font-size:10pt;">Member, <A HREF="http://pub96.ezboard.com/beqcivismacto" title="Civis Macto Website" style="color:#ff0000;">Civis Macto</A></td></tr></table></td></tr></table>
